---
 drivers/clk/clk-qoriq.c | 179 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++----
 1 file changed, 164 insertions(+), 15 deletions(-)

--- a/drivers/clk/clk-qoriq.c
+++ b/drivers/clk/clk-qoriq.c
